width="300px"
tooltip="The Real Hunger Games™?"
source="
title Vegan Nutrition
repeat
while (Hungry?) is (Yes)
  :Eat Healthy;
  note right
    No Animal Products
    Certainly No Dairy
  end note
endwhile (No)
repeatwhile (Go To Sleep)
"/>"""/>
